profile:
MOST TRUSTED PAINTING & DECORATING COMPANY!
 
We are a full service locally owned Painting & Decorating and Restoration Company with a full service Interior Designer. Budget & Save Painters is dedicated to providing exceptional Painting & Decorating Solutions to residential and commercial clients throughout the Metro Vancouver area.
 
Service Areas: all of Metro Vancouver including: Burnaby, Downtown Vancouver, Yaletown, the West End, Coal Harbour, Kitsilano, Dunbar, UBC, Kerrisdale, Shaughnessy, Richmond, Delta, Surrey, the North Shore including, (the British Properties, West Vancouver, and Deep Cove), Coquitlam area, Port Coquitlam, New Westminster, and Langley.
 
We Specialize in Color Consultations, and Interior Designs for Residential & Commercial Projects, Condos, Town-homes, Apartments, Design, Heritage Homes, Small repair jobs, and Maintenance of painting services!
 
Our Customer Service lines are available 24 hours a day - 7 days a week. We always provide references of our many satisfied customers. We use Top Quality Paints, Primers & Stains! Zero VOC Products - Our Business rating with the Better Business Bureau is A+. Look for our continually GREAT PROMOTIONAL DISCOUNTS - CALL FOR A FREE NO OBLIGATION ESTIMATION!
 
Great reliable painters!
Top-Line General Paint, Benjamin Moore Paints, Cloverdale, ICI Paints & Sherwin-Williams. Other Suggested Brands Offered. TOP QUALITY PAINTS, PRIMERS & STAINS. We use the right brands for each project!
Full Interior & Exterior Painting - Commercial projects and Residential projects - Drywall Repairs -Power Washing and Waterproofing. Colour Consultations - GREAT DISCOUNTS OFFERED!
Most brands supplied - Customer brands on request.
Specializing in Condos, Strata's, Multi-residential, Heritage homes, Maintenance, Tenant Improvements, Additions, Renovating, Changes or Moves & Complete Home Projects. SMALL JOBS WELCOME!
 
Our outstanding services have been catering to a number of locations across Metro Vancouver including Whistler, North Shore, Burnaby, Delta, Richmond, the city of Surrey, Langley Coquitlam, Port Coquitlam and many other outline areas. We are experts in providing exceptional customer service in painting & decorating for our residential and commercial clients throughout Metro Vancouver.
 
We are strong believers in safe (ZERO VOC) paint products and practices that save money, and are good for the environment. Budget & Save Painters and Creative Design offers a full range of luxury paint products.
 
We understand that when we are working on your house, you are inviting us into your home. Trust is of the utmost importance to us; we have an impeccable reputation with many local satisfied customers over the years, and being a fully insured company with WCB coverage, so you can feel confident that the construction process will run seamlessly and efficiently. Some have even gone as far as to say that they have enjoyed the process while working with us.
 
We specialize in Color Consulting, Custom Design/Decorating, Full Interior and Exterior Projects, Renovations, Pressure Washing and full Property Maintenance.

profile:
We LOVE kitchens!  As a team who cooks, bakes and loves to create – we want your kitchen to be the happy place in your house too. You could call us the kitchen nerds.  We are always up to date on the newest technologies and space-saving solutions and work to blend those with livability and comfort. Our first step is a comprehensive consultation to help best achieve your vision while working with the budget and space. We listen actively to ensure the design suits you, your home and how it's intended to function.

We will create a beautiful conceptual design based on measurements and create the best layout and design for you and how your household functions. We provide a spec book, construction drawings and samples as needed for your contractor and cabinet maker.  We are happy to liaise with your contracting service but are not construction experts.

6+ years of experience, BID from a CIDA accredited program and National Kitchen and Bath Association member.

profile:
At Vancouver General Contractors our mission is to provide our clients with an amazing experience in transforming their home into beautiful functional art that reflects the lifestyle they choose to lead. Vancouver General Contractors’ entire process is geared towards putting the customer first. Vancouver General Contractors’ Code of Business Practices ensures ethics and integrity are at the top of our priority list when serving our clients.  We offer a fixed price, and a two-year warranty on our work, so the customer knows we are working for them. We strive to educate the customer through the complexities of the construction industry and build process to ensure the customer realizes their dream and their budget!

We are an award winning company specializing in green-built projects, mobility accessibility, custom homes, additions and major renovations. Call us for a free onsite consultation and we will bring your vision to life!

profile:
Pure Luxe Painting is a top-tier painting company servicing the Vancouver Area. 

INTRODUCTION:
Pure Luxe Painting is Vancouver's premier full-service painting company, focused on providing unbeatable customer service and top-tier workmanship - all at affordable prices. 

"FULL-SERVICE" PAINTING COMPANY:
Our commercial painters and residential painters work with clients from the design stage right through to completion of any interior or exterior design project. 

INTERIOR DESIGNERS:
We have excellent interior designers that work with our clients to come up with a color scheme that works for you and your home. 

TOP-TIER QUALITY:
Right from your first meeting with our estimator you will see the difference in our quality, communication and service that we provide. 

PROFESSIONAL ESTIMATES:
Once you select Pure Luxe Painting for your project you can expect to receive a detailed project outline that will include the start day, estimated completion date, as well as the contact details of the project manager and lead painter on site for your project. 

LOCATIONS:
We provide our services to Vancouver, West Vancouver,North Vancouver, Richmond, Burnaby, New Westminster, Coquitlam, Port Moody, Port Coquitlam, Surrey, Langley, Abbotsford, Delta, South Surrey, White Rock, Tsawwassen, Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Whistler, and Squamish.
